{
  "texts": [
    "This approach accounts for the multifaceted nature of clinical decision-making and equips models to handle diverse and complex situations effectively.",
    "The comparison with specialists highlights the urgent need for supportive tools to decide in emergency situations.",
    "Surgeons may misclassify specific images due to various factors.",
    "Among the main reasons is the many images' poor quality, making it difficult for surgeons to evaluate them accurately.",
    "Inadequate lighting or low contrast can obscure bony structures, making diagnosis difficult."
  ]
}